title: Pro cliff jumpers take the plunge at McCloud Falls
text: Cliff jumpers take the plunge at McCloud Falls Feb 24, 2017 Freestyle cliff jumper Donny Beck filmed his brother Brandon Beck taking the plunge at an overflowing McCloud Falls in McCloud, California approximately 200 miles north of Sacramento, on February 12, 2017.
